{"tid":1058980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[童年回憶] 有冇人記得東涌foodcourt有個遊樂場","createTime":"2019-03-13T00:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T09:31:31.000Z","uid":178190,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf192108d37377f6eda5031ea07cfe367098773","tid":1058980,"uid":178190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:33:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人記得大概10年前<br />\n東涌東薈城裏面個foodcourt有個遊樂場仔<br />\n印象中係外太空theme<br />\n細個到而家都有啲印象<br />\n因為好少可食肆裏面有野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n十年冇去過東薈城<br />\n呢幾年好似拆咗<br />\nGoogle又搵唔到相<br />\n好似自己記錯咁<br />\n唔肯定係咪以前真係有啲咁既野<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以確定個度以前有個遊樂場<br />\n定係我真係記錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖如下: (畫得唔好唔好屌)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2dXB6Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2dXB6Y.png&h=69e468c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d7c0db0f204dc0e4f73211b0d161289aa366cdb","tid":1058980,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:52:46.000Z","msg":"個太空艙有陣臭味 唔識形容 好似鼻屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b28ef4b5ab034f2ff7a530f799378241c41600","tid":1058980,"uid":178190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"糾結咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲可以話我知完我心願"},{"pid":"376a6c5f9a4645cf80fd20f3b900c4bf24582c92","tid":1058980,"uid":38737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:53:29.000Z","msg":"Btw畫得好撚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c399ad9febb40cfef015c56d9e961b3e840656","tid":1058980,"uid":178190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d7c0db0f204dc0e4f73211b0d161289aa366cdb","tid":1058980,"uid":38737,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:52:46.000Z","msg":"個太空艙有陣臭味 唔識形容 好似鼻屎味<img src=\"